Nadeem Ahmed has broken the record for most catches (10) in ODIs for HKG, going past Babar Hayat's 9

stories.title: Tom Sole sinks Hong Kong with 4 for 15
stories.subTitle: Hong Kong v Scotland, Group B, ICC World Cup Qualifier
stories.seoTitle: Tom Sole sinks Hong Kong with 4 for 15
stories.summary: The offspinner restricted Hong Kong to just 91, and then the Scotland captain Kyle Coetzer led his side to their second win in two matches
